# Koreazar — Cursor context exclusions
# Keeps project-memory/ and project-authored markdown; drops vendor/generated noise.

# --- Dependencies (duplicate trees) ---
node_modules/
mobile/node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# --- Build & autogenerated output ---
dist/
dist-ssr/
mobile/.expo/
mobile/builds/
release/
build/
app/build/
.gradle/
*.apk
*.aab

# --- Logs, cache, temp ---
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
.cache/
.tmp/
temp/
tmp/
.turbo/
.vercel/

# --- Vendor & third-party asset trees ---
vendor/
**/vendor/
api/google/vendor/
api/google/**/vendor/
admin/assets/vendors/

# --- Rich-text editor bundles & their docs (vendor) ---
**/ckeditor/
**/CKEditor/
**/tinymce/
**/TinyMCE/
admin/assets/vendors/ckeditor/
admin/assets/vendors/tinymce/

# --- Markdown: vendor / generated only (not repo docs) ---
node_modules/**/*.md
dist/**/*.md
mobile/.expo/**/*.md
vendor/**/*.md
**/vendor/**/*.md
api/google/vendor/**/*.md
admin/assets/vendors/**/*.md
**/ckeditor/**/*.md
**/tinymce/**/*.md

# --- Explicit keeps (project memory & docs) ---
!project-memory/
!project-memory/**
!docs/
!docs/**
!README.md
!mobile/README.md
!mobile/docs/
!mobile/docs/**
!mobile/screenshots-source/README.md
!MEMORY_ANALYSIS_REPORT.md
